{"tid":1736003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"校長代表協調 18歲以下學生警方不即場拘捕 其餘由校長陪同登記被捕","createTime":"2019-11-18T16:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T16:28:05.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e1bcd0a5eafdfa792773ca16c52949bc0975bdb4","tid":1736003,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:22:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3553157598058170&amp;id=139543009419663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3553157598058170%26id%3D139543009419663&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=2d117845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3553157598058170&amp;id=139543009419663</a><br />\n<br />\n【校長代表協調 18歲以下學生警方不即場拘捕】<br />\n<br />\n到深夜時分，仍有大批黑衣人在理工大學校園內被警方圍堵。最新消息稱，校長代表經與警方協調後，警方對18歲以下學生不作即場拘捕，但18歲以上會立即拘捕，校長可陪同拘捕過程，律師會到登記地點協助。<br />\n<br />\n（立場新聞影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n#信報 #理大衝突"},{"pid":"89033eb7625b4c25881327d6f46103a1db44de4a","tid":1736003,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:24:44.000Z","msg":"[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d94818a26b92ff7375421c00ada7092d2dfcebcc","tid":1736003,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:26:02.000Z","msg":"不即場拘捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340c80ad32ddb69a538efd35a63c738f851443dc","tid":1736003,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T16:28:05.000Z","msg":"出咁多口術擺明係因為狗唔夠膽強攻<br />\n死守一定贏 拉都唔會俾人拉<br />\n手足一定要死守 點都唔好出"}]}